text: Kultay-Karan () is a rural locality (a village) in Bogdanovsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 204 as of 2010. There are 4 streets. == Geography == It is located 31 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki, 10 km from Bogdanovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Kultay-Karan
